<title>安装 SyncTeX</title>
<p>为了添加对 SyncTeX 的支持，下列软件包需要被安装:</p>
<list>
  <item>
    <p>
      A LaTeX engine with SyncTeX support, such as <app>pdflatex</app>.
    </p>
  </item>
  <item>
    <p>
      A text editor with SyncTeX support, such as <app>gedit</app> with gedit-plugins installed.
    </p>
  </item>
</list>

<p>在 <app>gedit</app>, 启用 SyncTex 插件：</p>
<steps>
   <item>
    <p>单击 <guiseq><gui>编辑</gui><gui>首选项</gui><gui>插件</gui></guiseq>。</p>
   </item>
   <item>
    <p>单击 <gui>SyncTeX</gui>。</p>
   </item>
</steps>
